### 1. 그룹 생성
POST http://localhost:3000/api/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "group",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.png",
  "isPublic": true,
  "introduction": "This is a group."
}

### 2. 그룹 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/api/groups?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=latest HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 특정 그룹 조회 (존재 확인용)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/groups/8/is-public HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. 그룹 수정
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/groups/8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated group",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/new-image.png",
  "isPublic": false,
  "introduction": "This is an updated group."
}

### 5. 그룹 공감하기
POST http://localhost:3000/api/groups/8/like HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. 그룹 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/groups/8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "securepassword123"
}
